article.headline: Acuff scores 23 as Eastern Michigan downs Central Arkansas 74-71
article.description: — Tyson Acuff had 23 points in Eastern Michigan's 74-71 win against Central Arkansas on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Acuff scores 23 as Eastern Michigan downs Central Arkansas 74-71
article.story: CONWAY, Ark. -- — Tyson Acuff had 23 points in Eastern Michigan's 74-71 win against Central Arkansas on Saturday night. Acuff added five rebounds for the Eagles (4-2). Arne Osojnik scored 20 points and added five rebounds. Yusuf Jihad was 4-of-8 shooting (3 for 4 from 3-point range) to finish with 12 points. Carl Daughtery Jr. led the Bears (1-6) in scoring, finishing with 24 points and three steals. Javion Guy-King added 14 points and two steals for Central Arkansas. In addition, Masai Olowokere finished with 12 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
